And on December 10th

1145
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:48,000
I'm gonna go back to Toronto

1146
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:50,000
And I'm gonna drive my car

1147
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:52,000
And I will see you in February

1148
