Blessed be the name of the Lord

1156
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:12,000
Let's pray together

1157
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:14,000
As the worship team comes up

1158
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:16,000
Heavenly Father

1159
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:18,000
We thank you for the story of Joseph

1160
